<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Diary</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- 다이어리 스타일시트 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/menu.css"> <!-- 메뉴 스타일시트 -->
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="/images/spring_logo.png" alt="Spring Logo"/>
            </div>
            <h1>Spring</h1>
            <nav>
                <ul class="menu">
                    <li><a href="#"><img src="/images/board.png" alt="Board"/>게시판</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><img src="/images/test.png" alt="Test"/>테스트</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><img src="/images/prescription.png" alt="Prescription"/>복용약</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><img src="/images/sleep.png" alt="Sleep"/>수면</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><img src="/images/exercise.png" alt="Exercise"/>운동</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><img src="/images/diary.png" alt="Diary"/>일기</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="user-menu">
                    <button class="user-button">로그아웃</button>
                    <button class="user-button">회원 정보 수정</button>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main>
            <section class="diary-entry">
                <div class="photo">
                    <div class="photo-frame">
                        <img id="photo-of-the-day" src="image_placeholder.jpg" alt="Photo of the day">
                        <button class="photo-button" onclick="addPhoto()">+</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="entry">
                    <label for="date">날짜:</label>
                    <input type="date" id="date" name="date">
                    <label for="weather">날씨:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="weather" name="weather" placeholder="오늘의 날씨">
                    <textarea id="diary-text" placeholder="여기에 일기를 작성하세요."></textarea>
                    <div class="buttons">
                        <button class="view-all-button">일기 전체보기</button>
                        <button class="save-button">저장하기</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <div id="all-entries" class="all-entries">
            <header>
                <h2>2024년 4월</h2>
            </header>
            <section class="calendar">
                <input type="date" id="entry-date" name="entry-date">
                <button onclick="viewEntry()">보기</button>
            </section>
            <section id="previous-entry" class="previous-entry">
                <div class="photo">
                    <img src="previous_image.jpg" alt="Previous entry photo">
                </div>
                <div class="entry">
                    <p>선택된 날짜의 일기가 여기에 표시됩니다.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="scripts.js"></script> <!-- 아직 작성되지 않은 JavaScript 파일 -->
</body>
</html>
